data.title: Merryall Benefit barbra & Litmus Fusion Jazz
data.meta_description:
barbra & Litmus - WPKN | MERRYALL BENEFIT

barbra is a power trio of saxophone, bass, and drums playing experimental jazz with punk roots and some ska influence. Their material is fun and sonically powerful, using heavy effects and modular synths to create a driving, forceful, yet playful style.
